    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Chat HILT status mix over time",
      "description": "Status counters from RecordGuardrailEvaluation(\"openclaw:hilt\", action). Stack shows requested vs approved/denied/timeout/unsupported simultaneously so you can see the operator-response funnel.\n\ncovered_by:\n  - defenseclaw_guardrail_evaluations \u2192 internal/telemetry/metrics.go (RecordGuardrailEvaluation)",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "defenseclaw-prometheus"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 12,
        "w": 12,
        "h": 8
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum by (guardrail_action_taken) (rate(defenseclaw_guardrail_evaluations_total{guardrail_scanner=\"openclaw:hilt\"}[$__rate_interval]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{guardrail_action_taken}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "cps",
          "custom": {
            "stacking": {
              "mode": "normal"
            },
            "fillOpacity": 25
          }
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Chat HILT approval-vs-denial rate (1h rolling)",
      "description": "approved / (approved + denied + timeout). Slow drift toward 0 means operators are denying more often \u2014 investigate via the verdict-categories panel on Security.\n\ncovered_by:\n  - defenseclaw_guardrail_evaluations \u2192 internal/telemetry/metrics.go (RecordGuardrailEvaluation)",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "defenseclaw-prometheus"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 12,
        "y": 12,
        "w": 12,
        "h": 8
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(rate(defenseclaw_guardrail_evaluations_total{guardrail_scanner=\"openclaw:hilt\", guardrail_action_taken=\"approval_approved\"}[1h])) / clamp_min(sum(rate(defenseclaw_guardrail_evaluations_total{guardrail_scanner=\"openclaw:hilt\", guardrail_action_taken=~\"approval_approved|approval_denied|approval_timeout\"}[1h])), 0.0001)",
          "legendFormat": "approval rate",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "percentunit",
          "min": 0,
          "max": 1
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Pending requests gauge (5m window)",
      "description": "Approximation of in-flight requests = requested - (approved + denied + timeout) summed over the last 5 minutes. Sustained positive value means operators are slow to respond. Negative or zero means the queue is clear.\n\ncovered_by:\n  - defenseclaw_guardrail_evaluations \u2192 internal/telemetry/metrics.go (RecordGuardrailEvaluation)",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "defenseclaw-prometheus"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 20,
        "w": 8,
        "h": 6
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "clamp_min(sum(increase(defenseclaw_guardrail_evaluations_total{guardrail_scanner=\"openclaw:hilt\", guardrail_action_taken=\"approval_requested\"}[5m])) - sum(increase(defenseclaw_guardrail_evaluations_total{guardrail_scanner=\"openclaw:hilt\", guardrail_action_taken=~\"approval_approved|approval_denied|approval_timeout\"}[5m])), 0) or vector(0)",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "orange",
                "value": 5
              },
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": 20
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      },
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "area"
      }
    },
